verbose_text: RT-PCR and real-time PCR showed that 4-PBA significantly attenuated the tunicamycin induced expressions of MUC5AC and MUC5B mRNA (XREF_FIG - XREF_FIG), ELISA also showed that 4-PBA significantly attenuated the tunicamycin induced productions of MUC5AC and MUC5B glycoproteins (XREF_FIG).
